      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) with documented verification test suite; version-controlled case files stored in institutional repository.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is a commercially validated solver with published verification benchmarks. Case files are version-controlled under Git with commit hashes recorded in the simulation log. SQA level exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
