      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes standard benchmark cases (lid-driven cavity, pipe flow) at published accuracy levels.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verification test suite results for laminar and turbulent pipe flow, lid-driven cavity, and rotating machinery benchmarks reviewed. All pass within published solver tolerances. No custom solver modifications applied."
