      "rationale": "Blood modeled as Newtonian fluid (viscosity 0.0035 Pa·s, density 1060 kg/m³) consistent with published CPB CFD practice. Giersiepen-Wurzinger coefficients (α=3.62×10⁻⁷, β=2.416, C=0.785) taken from original publication. Material property traceability documented in simulation report Appendix B."
    },
